    <comment>- update to 0.3.7:
  * Add Python 3.12 builds
  * Fix `__libsoxr_version__` (https://github.com/dofuuz/python-
    soxr/pull/22)
  * Fix version importing for setuptools_scm&lt;7 (Fix #21)
- update to 0.3.6:
  * Add __libsoxr_version__ to check version of linked libsoxr

  * Deprecate implicit dtype conversion</comment>
